title: Election Night Preview, FL Rep. Neal Dunn
itunes:title: Election Night Preview, FL Rep. Neal Dunn
description:
Guests: Mark Niquette, Bloomberg National political reporter, Kriti Gupta, Bloomberg Markets Live reporter, Jen Psaki, Former Communitions Director for the Obama Administration, Tyler Deaton, Republican strategist, fundraiser, and President of Allegiance Strategies, and Rep. Neal Dunn, a Republican representing Florida's 2nd congressional district.
